1. *Spasili* smo mačku koja se penjala po drvetu. (We saved the cat that was climbing the tree.)
2. Upravo su *spasili* turiste koji su se izgubili u planinama. (They have just rescued the tourists who were lost in the mountains.)
3. Moramo da *spasemo* ljude koji su ugroženi u poplavama. (We need to rescue people who are endangered by floods.)
4. *Spašavajući* devojčicu iz požara, vatrogasci su pokazali hrabrost. (By rescuing the little girl from the fire, firefighters showed courage.)
5. Oni su nam *spasili* živote kada smo se izgubili u šumi. (They saved our lives when we were lost in the forest.)
6. Pokušali su da *spase* pticu koja se povredila na ulici. (They tried to save the bird that was injured on the street.)
7. Kada su videli da se brod prevrće, oni su brzo *spasili* sve putnike. (When they saw that the boat was capsizing, they quickly saved all the passengers.)
8. Ne znam kako da *spasim* ovaj dokument, izgleda da je oštećen. (I don't know how to save this document, it seems to be damaged.)
9. Uzalud su pokušavali da *spase* izgubljenu turu. (They tried in vain to save the lost sheep.)
10. Sve više ljudi shvata koliko je važno *spasavati* životinje koje su ugrožene. (More and more people realize how important it is to save endangered animals.)